{"type": "article", "id": 6232, "title": "Duetta 双人车", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-15T07:53:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052342144YjeCE3yUJ8TfFQB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计机构 Sentidos 日前推出了一款可供双人骑行的自行车，名为 Duetta。设计团队为这款双人自行车配置了双踏板，可供两人同时蹬踏，可为情侣、家人或者朋友间创造协作骑行的乐趣。Duetta 的前座与副座皆是可调节式的，除了供双人骑乘的功能以外，也可用于单人骑行。设计者的本意是为了分享，激发与营造一种令人愉快的骑行体验。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234212DXZarOefl09VdYWv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234212vlC0oiWAse2gk5OY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5265625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234212QEJSLgX6ObicGwfN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052342135rTjxMzYkg4PtBwG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234213UT59Gfxu2riVPdJF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}